			<CASNumber>7446-19-7</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Zinc sulfate monohydrate is a hydrate form of zinc sulfate, an inorganic compound combining sulfur and zinc. It is highly soluble in water and used in various applications due to its versatility and beneficial properties. Zinc sulfate is essential for the function of numerous enzymes, contributing to antioxidant activities, brain function, and immune system support. It is commonly used to reduce the duration of respiratory infections and the common cold, and is found in various forms such as powders, granules, pellets, and tablets.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硫酸锌一水合物是硫酸锌的水合物形式，硫酸锌是一种结合硫和锌的无机化合物。它在水中高度可溶，由于其多功能性和有益的特性，可用于各种应用。硫酸锌对许多酶的功能至关重要，有助于抗氧化活性、大脑功能和免疫系统支持。它通常用于减少呼吸道感染和普通感冒的持续时间，并以各种形式存在，如粉末、颗粒、颗粒和片剂。</common:generalComment>
